## Engine [/api/v1.0/vehicles/{id}/engine]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1234 (string) - Vehicle ID

### Start Engine [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "action": "START"
        }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)

        {
          "status": "success|error"
        }

+ Response 400

+ Response 404

+ Response 500

### Stop Engine [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "action": "STOP"
        }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)

        {
          "status": "success|error"
        }

+ Response 400

+ Response 404

+ Response 500
